name: Nike Women Lunarswift +3 Sports Shoes
description:
A take off from the classic LunarGlide, the nike LunarSwift+ 3 running shoe for women offers absolute cushioned comfort, better Fit and dynamic support. Perfect for underpronators and moderate overpronators, the Dynamic Support platform in the midsole adapts to the runner's varying stride and offers on-demand support. Featuring a nike+ Ready option, this shoe can be teamed with Nike+ compatible iPods, stop watches and much more to clock your fitness regime.

Upper
Breathable mesh upper with a nearly seamless construction for ample ventilation and reduced irritation
Inner bootie that wraps around the foot offering exceptional comfort
Extended Flywire panels for lightweight comfort, super strong support and more secure fit around the midfoot and heel
Symmetrical lace-up system for a snug fit
Meshed and padded tongue and sockliner for in-step comfort
Perforated, internal fit saddle work with lacing system for a comfortable, snug fit

Midsole
FitSole cushioning for ultra-lightweight, springy cushioning and soft, responsive shock absorption
Dynamic Support system to adapt to your stride
Padded footbed for all-day comfort
Removable footbed to accommodate an orthotic

Outsole
Environmentally preferred rubber outsole for enhanced durability
Carbon rubber under the heel for abrasion resistance
Waffle pattern for maximum traction, with a scooped heel for extra cushioning

Shoe care
Wipe surface with damp, clean cloth to remove dust
Do not machine wash or store in direct sunlight

name: Nike Men T90 Exacto Sports Shoes
description:
Choose the nike T90 Exacto IV for power and accuracy. Designed for the elite player who kicks with force and passes with purpose, the nike T90 Exacto Soccer Cleat is built to overpower the competition on harder natural surfaces.

Upper
Synthetic leather upper for comfort and great ball feel
Shot shield aids in performance on instep/swerve striking and shot accuracy
Lateral plastic support helps lock down the heel for a secure Fit and also helps to stabilize the planting foot when kicking the ball
Off-center lacing system is designed to provide a larger ball striking surface for more uniform cleat-to-ball contact

Midsole
Instep pods deliver even pressure on the ball at impact for optimal precision at high speeds
High-density EVA sockliner provides contoured heel and arch support and reduces cleat pressure

Outsole
Firm-ground cleats for use on short-grass fields that may be slightly wet but rarely muddy
Forefoot flex groove enhances flexibility for a more natural, efficient range of motion

shoe care
Wipe surface with damp, clean cloth to remove dust
Do not machine wash or store in direct sunlight
